KB001 — How to Collect Event Logs for Troubleshooting
Purpose:  
Provide technicians with a standardized method for collecting Windows event logs when diagnosing crashes, login failures, update issues, or system instability.

🧭 Steps
Open Event Viewer  
Press Win + R, type eventvwr.msc, press Enter.

Export System Logs  
Navigate to:
Windows Logs → System → Save All Events As…

Export Application Logs  
Navigate to:
Windows Logs → Application → Save All Events As…

Export Security Logs  
Navigate to:
Windows Logs → Security → Save All Events As…

Export Windows Update Logs  
Navigate to:
Applications and Services Logs → Microsoft → Windows → WindowsUpdateClient → Operational

Export Crash / WER Logs  
Navigate to:
Applications and Services Logs → Microsoft → Windows → WER-SystemErrorReporting → Operational

